; Coverage test for post.cc
; Tests get_price when a posting has an annotation with a price.
; When amount has annotation with price, get_price returns the price.
; When no annotation, get_price falls back to get_cost.

2024/03/01 Purchase
    Expenses:Food     100 EUR @ $1.10
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(price)\n"
$110
$-110
end test
